      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-acc-ric-sel      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione status impostazione             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-sts-imp-ric      .
